{"word":"σιτέομαι","slug":"σιτέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σιτέομαι</b></el> <el>(σιτέομαι,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σῖτος'><el>σῖτος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to take food, eat</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to feed on, eat</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ς. ἐλπίδας</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>τὴν σοφίαν</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}